      "content": "That's a good start for the atmosphere. To make it more immersive for the script, I want to get more specific about the \"tension\" I mentioned. Can you expand on the description of the people hanging around? I want to ground the danger in the actual characters there—what do they look like, what are they wearing, and what kind of vibe do they give off that makes someone feel like they shouldn't be walking through there alone?",
